The report shall include the following information:
For each approved motion picture or entertainment production project:
The name of the approved company and a brief description of the project;
The amount of approved costs included in the agreement; and
The total amount recovered under the tax incentive agreement;
The number of applications for projects submitted during the prior fiscal year;
The number of projects finally approved during the prior fiscal year; and
The total dollar amount approved for recovery for all projects approved during the prior fiscal year, and cumulatively under KRS 141.383 and 148.542 to 148.546 since its inception, by year of approval.
